it.unipr.netsec.ipstack.ip4

Interface IpAddressPrefix

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Address, IpAddress
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Ip4AddressPrefix, Ip6AddressPrefix

    public interface IpAddressPrefix
extends IpAddress
    Internet Protocol version 4 (IPv4) address with prefix length.

    It extends class Ip4Address by simply adding prefix length information.
